{"tid":998650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高登聲明絕不會用阿里雲，亦不會上傳資料予政權，中資機構等","createTime":"2019-01-28T06:23:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-28T14:26:26.000Z","uid":133680,"like":12,"dislike":53,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"44705bad4fe3c1acb28941e0c7ee77bb199f14dd","tid":998650,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T06:23:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=7011356&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D7011356%26page%3D1&d=%2B6PerixXDkZX5A3TLqthDm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=1ccc01b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=7011356&amp;page=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/01/22/3WlxoX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F01%2F22%2F3WlxoX.png&h=b3b1492e&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n高登即將推出新網頁版，新版將會兼容desktop、tablet同mobile，現階段開放試用版予過去一年活躍會員試用，歡迎各位提供意見，同時開發人員亦會於期間完善網頁版功能及改善用戶體驗，試用版網頁將不定期更新。 <br />\n<br />\n獲邀請試用新網頁版嘅會員將收到專人pm，可以用現有嘅高登會員帳戶登入以下網站。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://newweb.hkgolden.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewweb.hkgolden.com%2F&d=%2B6PerixXDkZX5A3TLqthDm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=52c8c3eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://newweb.hkgolden.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n如有任何此意見或問題，可於此帖留言或telegram: gwangung1991<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>【道歉啟事】有關新網頁UI framework事宜</strong></span><br />\n新網頁封測期間，有會員表示對網站UI framework使用Ant Design作為界面設計用途有所疑惑，其後開發者團隊因欠深思熟慮而作出易導致他人誤會的言論，並引起爭議，故此感到萬分抱歉，懇求各位會員原諒。在此官方保證將改用Google的Material UI開發，而因轉換framework需時，新網頁將暫不作更新，現時受邀請封測的會員仍然可以操作現有的新版本網頁，並繼續提供意見。<br />\n<br />\n又及，現嚴正聲明，高登<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">絕不會使用阿里雲進行網頁hosting</span></span>，亦<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">從沒有上傳資料予任何政權、中資或相關組織</span></span>，高登將捍衛每位會員的言論自由，還望各會員務必相信高登管理團隊。另外有會員指出alicdn網址為svg symbol script，作用為顯示新網頁icon之用，其為framework所使用之icon庫平台而產生的script檔案，由於該檔案使用alicdn服務或令會員有所憂慮，開發團隊已移除相關網址並改用本地伺服器進行相關存取。<br />\n<br />\n對是次新網頁版測試令不少會員感到疑慮或不安，我們再次深深致歉，此後我們將更謹慎選擇一切有關建構高登討論區的程式，並加強各方溝通，避免跟會員出現不必要的磨擦。<br />\n<br />\n感激一直以來支持高登討論區的每一位會員。誠惶誠恐，懇請原諒。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【封測】高登討論區重製新網頁版(1):<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=MB&amp;message=7010349\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DMB%26message%3D7010349&d=%2B6PerixXDkZX5A3TLqthDm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=f4947457\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=MB&amp;message=7010349</a>"},{"pid":"48794fadcd03887ae7d4ee4fa64c3631047e2569","tid":998650,"uid":108201,"like":51,"dislike":1,"score":50,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T06:24:39.000Z","msg":"關我地撚事呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7bb789dd0fbf9d55c6b6b661c314afbd2f9c479","tid":998650,"uid":1977,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T06:27:00.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"4fec0ac2b851742c2bf577f659c6598a81e9b54d","tid":998650,"uid":522,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T06:30:35.000Z","msg":"次次整單柒事出黎"},{"pid":"d1bc79ab2f20b796bec3a44643d8e658b93694c6","tid":998650,"uid":37136,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T06:31:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a970bc0afcf618bc23f3a4445ae81f750066902b","tid":998650,"uid":65328,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T06:32:22.000Z","msg":"幾個月後， 已成歷史文件"},{"pid":"73a2e1ca0ce0dae09cf4075843d2a31523e6a850","tid":998650,"uid":89514,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T06:32:3